    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are acceptable at this risk level per ASME V&V 40 Table 1. The CFD model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index criterion RH < 1 is satisfied across all five operating points.",
